data.description: Beautiful Chalet home located in Wallenpaupack Lake Estates, an amenity filled community in The Northern Poconos with lakerights to Lake Wallenpaupack.  This gorgeous 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom chalet home has CENTRAL A/C, an open floor plan, a great room with cathedral ceilings, hardwood floors, a stone faced corner fireplace, a loft overlooking the living room, and new stainless steel appliances in the kitchen.  The master bedroom has a master bathroom with a jacuzzi.  The main level includes a half bath and laundry room with new washer and dryer, access to the large wrap around deck.   The lower level family room has a reclaimed wood look accent wall, the heated garage is finished with RaceDeck Diamond Plate Flooring.  The home is in a convenient location on a nice level lot.
